p}$ and\n$\\mathrm{PresPower}$, we believe our algorithm provides new intuition for the\ndecidability of these theories, and for the features that lead to\nnon-elementary blow-ups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 May 2023 17:57:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-05"}
