 whereas a specific chemical structure of AHA\nengenders marginal differences. The rationalization of the energy reaction\nprofiles is given in terms of partial atomic charges, geometrical\npeculiarities, steric barriers, imaginary vibrational frequencies, and related\ndescriptors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 May 2023 18:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-08"}
