ction and tracking. In our real-world\nevaluation on a two-way traffic road with 1120 virtual sensors, TelecomTM\nachieved 90.18% vehicle detection accuracy, 27$\\times$ and 5$\\times$ error\nreduction for vehicle position and speed tracking compared to a baseline\nmethod, and $\\pm$3.92% and $\\pm$11.98% percent error for vehicle wheelbase and\nweight estimation, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 May 2023 21:45:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-08"}
