 RXs. Finally, our numerical results highlight that the proposed optimal\ndistribution of the transmit signal yields significantly higher achievable\ninformation rates compared to uniformly distributed transmit signals, which are\noptimal for linear optical information RXs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 May 2023 13:31:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-08"}
